We recommended that the Management:
Reconcile the noted differences and require the GSO/Property Officer to document all unaccounted properties and reconcile their records with accounting records.            
Prepare the necessary complete Report on the Physical Count of PPE to establish existence and validity. 
Maintain Property Ledger Card/Property Cards update adequate accounting and property records and conduct periodic reconciliation between accounting and property records;
Exert efforts to locate all properties and records and conduct a thorough physical check and inventory of all properties. All unserviceable properties should be properly reported to serve as basis for dropping in the books of accounts by the Accounting Department;
Ensure strict adherence to the applicable laws, rules and regulations on PPE to prevent the incurrence of the deficiencies noted.

